Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:11.81,CMTS,NTP,0,0,0,,註: 真打是能在落語表演壓軸的名演員，前座是炒熱氣氛的新手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:55.07,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,很適合魔女的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.76,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,旅館的老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.68,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,好心把女兒的舊衣服送給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:04.66,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得有點緊不好活動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:06.74,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有木杖也靜不下心來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.08,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,在城市裡還請忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:11.12,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,很適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:13.97,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,打扮得還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:15.48,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:20.19,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,是能摧毀一個村落的可怕魔女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:22.55,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:26.89,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:29.24,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,這地方竟然有三個姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:30.80,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,有一個小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.81,0:22:32.84,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,這條真順
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:35.02,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣 來喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:36.02,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我拒絶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:39.32,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:40.65,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:42.52,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣就沒問題了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:44.73,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼在這地方喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.25,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:54.25,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,這是回禮 把我家人衣服弄髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:56.59,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,家人...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.84,0:23:00.76,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:04.02,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,這個城市...人類的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:07.93,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,無可救藥的粗野 愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:11.10,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿嘿 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.81,0:23:14.78,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,十分醜陋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.48,0:23:16.56,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:12.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:18.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是法王廳教圈的軍隊大集合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:25.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這份躁動的燒焦味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:28.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身體早已習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:30.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}這戰場的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:43.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:45.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:46.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是什麼穿著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:48.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來完全忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:54.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是法王廳教圈的主城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:56.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣不明所以的打扮是不能進城的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:01:00.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,官兵老爺 那是戲子的裝扮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:02.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雲遊藝人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:04.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是藝人 也不能放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:10.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:14.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說剛才的舉動也不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,赤裸裸的魔女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:18.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是注目的焦點了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:19.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:21.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:23.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個打扮還是不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:25.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不去哪裡買點普通衣服的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:28.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我這樣就是普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:30.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這會兒還較什麼勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:34.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:38.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:40.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,過分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:42.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個破帽子算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:44.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你把別人的勸告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:50.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 你這樣在街上亂走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那個魔女在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:57.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 多洛屁 你真混
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是 多洛皮啦 依巴蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:02.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個帽子和衣服都是芙羅拉親手縫製的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,其它全都燒光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:06.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,親手...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:08.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是遺物 遺物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:10.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓女孩子哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:11.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:16.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:19.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去找落腳的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:21.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你去把她帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:24.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:28.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:31.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:33.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:45.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託 那是什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:10.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 那傢伙的身體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:11.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微離開我一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:20.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難受 好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:29.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放下來 放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,解放我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:39.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人犯了什麼事被吊在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是小屁孩遊蕩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:49.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 這些人是庫夏人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是庫夏人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:54.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卻是住在巴利達尼斯的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:55.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隸?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:58.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個巴利達尼斯是商人的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:03.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在其他法王廳教圈的國家 庫夏人只是教敵而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:07.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而在這裡卻是商品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:12.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但這次的大戰卻不能再這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:19.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟這次巴利達尼斯被選為法王廳教圈的名譽鎮守府了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:23.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就這吊起來 用作昂揚鬥志的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:28.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就為了這種理由 這麼不講理的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人就要剝奪他人的生命嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:35.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,將骸骨捆綁對死者來說是褻瀆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:40.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就放下他們 進行火葬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也要幫忙 明白沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:06.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 史爾基 該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:08.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天要黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:23.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一整片森林的樹都拿來也肯定不夠用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,建造如此的龐然大物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:30.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些士兵要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:35.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為了血流成河 就聚集起那些人力物力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:40.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是屬於那些人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:48.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:55.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡被人類的嘈雜淹沒 精靈的聲音卻非常纖細
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:57.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,碼頭 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:02.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你朋友嗎 那最好快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那一帶天黑後很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:08.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,海盜假扮的武裝商船都集中在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:12.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被發現的話 會被綁架然後賣到外國去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:16.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在找魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:21.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:25.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那個魔女你要是知道什麼能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你這樣人要找魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想抓到魔女交給官差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:35.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為了自己出人頭地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:36.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,出人頭地?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:41.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別裝蒜了 你那打扮就是見習騎士的貴族少爺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:45.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想立個功然後去封個騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你想的美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:48.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會讓你得逞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:53.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等啊 我的話還沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:04.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基 我肚子餓了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:10.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有魔女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是魔女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:22.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能 看出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:29.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你戴著尖帽子和木杖啊 還和動物說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:31.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這個小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著妖精的女子一定是魔女了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:37.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你能看到我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:38.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有剛才那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:46.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你解放了那些被吊著的庫夏人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你那些也能看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:55.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥啊 對那些大人隨意玩弄 那就是魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不是那麼不得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:02.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但魔女不是住在森林或是山上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼到這來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:06.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在旅行中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:07.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有這個孩子在就是兩個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:14.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 來到這個城市後發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:22.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很辛苦呢 和其他的人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是這個城市的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:29.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也是發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 比如說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:34.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在某個地方有隻醜小鴨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:34.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,醜小鴨？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我知道這個故事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:41.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,醜小鴨因為和別人不同而被排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那隻醜小鴨其實是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天鵝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是鳶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:50.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天鴨子窩被一群壞心腸的烏鴉襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:57.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,弱小的鴨子無法飛離 結果都被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:04.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而鳶的孩子認為自己是鴨子 不知道如何飛走 也被抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:11.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那時救下鴨子們的是百鳥之王 白鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:13.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:17.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,白鷹帶領手下的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:20.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬間就把那些烏鴉幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:23.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹和鳶像親戚一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:28.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鳶的孩子此時才第一次遇到同伴 知道自己會飛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,後來呢 後來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:35.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,白鷹把在全國作亂的烏鴉全都趕走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:43.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是龍 鴨子們 甚至改變主意的烏鴉也跟隨白鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鳶的孩子很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:51.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只有自己能和鷹在同一片天空翱翔 感受同樣的風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 引人遐想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:04.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被烏鴉王抓住的鴨子公主 被白鷹救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小心翼翼的鴨子們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:14.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,希望透過自鷹和鴨子公主的聯姻而讓自己與白鷹的聯繫更深
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鳶的孩子卻不高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:23.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不爽的鳶的孩子凝望著大海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓自己的心情恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:31.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鳶的孩子在海上遇到了被海鷗包圍的森林的貓頭鷹的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:34.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鳶的孩子在想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:38.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被這麼多海鷗圍繞的貓頭鷹的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卻感覺有些寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:44.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有些相像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:50.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定能成為朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:57.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我 感覺像貓頭鷹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你身邊有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:08.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我身邊的人都是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:10.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法師的感受...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:17.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:18.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定戀愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:19.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定戀愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是那樣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:25.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只是對方是大人 又很關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才會向他撒嬌的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,給我站住 你們這群臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:38.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼 人口販子 海盜?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:39.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:42.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:45.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,害我們浪費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:47.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭哭啼啼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:50.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你們已經無處可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:59.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再在我面前做出這等難看的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:09.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小妞你這行頭是想扮魔女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:10.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:12.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們才是 肯定是海盜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:13.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,定是海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:16.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是想把這些孩子綁架到國外去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:19.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是沒了父母的庫夏人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:24.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能就這麼把他們扔到城裡不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:28.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 這裡被燒了也活該
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:34.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,城市的法律和商人的道理和我這魔女都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小丫頭騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:38.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你再這樣看不起我們就
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:41.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身體動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:47.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 魔法? 剛才那是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:49.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只是個暗示而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小丫頭騙子你做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:54.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是動不了我這拳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:00.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:03.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們這群海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:10.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集這麼多孩子難不成想去野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:12.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:19.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好 出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,砍人這是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:32.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看到同伴流血就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:34.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:36.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好老實待著小妞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不想受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:42.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:45.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你瞎認真什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:51.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 是想隱藏你的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他還挺硬氣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:56.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她能聽見念話?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:05.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:06.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能對付大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:09.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣遲早會被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:14.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,旅館都滿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:19.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老實把劍扔了還能留你一條狗命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:22.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把你打個半死然後吊在桅杆上一整天就饒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:30.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 小兄弟 亂管閒事會吃苦頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喵好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友受你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你也要動手嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真狠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:49.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不猶豫地砍下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:08.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為這樣才討厭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對上大人還不知道天高地厚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:16.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老大!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:18.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妥妥的海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:24.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了小鬼們 大人的社會有嚴格的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:29.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是觸犯了就得稍微懲罰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:34.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為海盜會更有骨氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,訓練得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:43.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正統派的貴族劍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:46.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:49.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小看大人可不行啊 小少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:03.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這年紀要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真打登場!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:11.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,前座就歇著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:22.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能在船上跟上我的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:26.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了 我可是每次都是在要摔倒的情況下揮劍的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:28.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不管什麼姿勢都能打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:37.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的劍裡沒有要取人性命的殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小子們 都帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:48.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,巴克 閃光!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:54.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:04.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是都是小孩子 但是待著這麼多庫夏人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:07.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一次都沒被盤問就出了城
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:13.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為 秘密 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:18.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 這些小孩要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:20.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,當然要帶回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:22.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又這麼擅自決定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,決定了 以我巫女的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:33.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不想給美好的回憶抹黑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:39.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我們的大將不是連這點小事就抱怨的心胸狹窄的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:40.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我說是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:43.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼蠢話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:49.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是偷來的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,赤手空拳能保護他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:57.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來把劍丟到海裡的不是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:59.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,丟臉 你這樣還騎士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:03.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是好像跌倒的青蛙一樣的醜態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:05.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是 船上跟個醉鬼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:06.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話 要不要跟我們一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:15.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:20.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:30.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你感覺在這個世界上沒有歸宿的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:32.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎你加入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:47.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝好意 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:10.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有要回去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:12.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:16.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的男人 那就是你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:20.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,切 被甩了啊 真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了 還沒問你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:27.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫索妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:28.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,依巴蕾拉唷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:35.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 漂亮的臉蛋被打扁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:40.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的臉才是像個爛肉包子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:41.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,干他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:46.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊 看來不把你牙都都得都都都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個 你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:49.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,閉上臭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:53.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是苗路 你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:55.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲多多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:58.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我記住你的名字了 伊茲多多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:19:59.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是伊茲多多!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:04.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基 儘快離開這座城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:15.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:21.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有緣再見 森林裡的貓頭鷹小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:25.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們也趕快快的回去去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:29.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去吧 門就要關了 要回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:38.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有帽子和那什麼什麼 對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:40.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 聽不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說人話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,帽子和衣服的事 不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:49.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是 任性不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:56.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 沒幫上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,走 盛飯了 盛飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看著我這邊都痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:20.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來都是 一臉壞人臉的人 沒有像樣點的旅館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:24.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 城裡都是士兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:27.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有旅館就謝天謝地了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:32.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,酒坊哪裡都一樣 賭博 打架 娼婦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:35.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐來喝一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:36.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我說大叔你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:38.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:42.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯的時候 不要把腳放在桌子上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:46.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:53.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:19.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:24.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裡 可以露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:36.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣繼續旅行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:42.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不久就會再次與使徒相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:48.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後那個時候 帶領他們的恐怕就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:50.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.84,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 小猴子
